casebody.data:
[*] LITTLE and LITTLE against FLEMING and FLEMING.

_OH CERTIORARI.

Issuing execution on report of referees without judgment, void.

The cause below had been referred; and on the coining in of the report of referees, the justice entered the same in his docket, and without entering judgment, issued execution. For this error, the proceedings below were ordered to be

Set aside, and declared null and void.
